<p>Today the flame stitch pattern is found on nearly every item imaginable. Remaining true to its roots, the embroidered flame stitch can be found on pillows, upholstery, and even draperies. Its colorful designs and intricate shading effects make it an instant eye-catcher. While there are nearly endless options now, there is no denying that this oldie has become a goodie. </p>
